    "start_blocks": "var correctPIN = \"9333\"; // You can change this\nvar input = \"\";\n\n// Simulate response time based on character match\nfunction simulateResponseTime(guess, target) {\n  var baseTime = 0.1;\n  var perCharDelay = 0.05;\n  var correctCount = 0;\n  \n  for (var i = 0; i < 4; i++) {\n    if (guess[i] === target[i]) {\n      correctCount++;\n    } else {\n      break;\n    }\n  }\n  \n  var noise = (Math.random() * 0.006) - 0.003;\n  var totalTime = baseTime + (correctCount * perCharDelay) + noise;\n  return Math.round(totalTime * 1000) / 1000;\n}\n\n// --- Number buttons ---\nonEvent(\"1_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  if (input.length < 4) {\n    input += \"1\";\n    updateScreen();\n  }\n});\nonEvent(\"2_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  if (input.length < 4) {\n    input += \"2\";\n    updateScreen();\n  }\n});\nonEvent(\"3_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  if (input.length < 4) {\n    input += \"3\";\n    updateScreen();\n  }\n});\nonEvent(\"4_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  if (input.length < 4) {\n    input += \"4\";\n    updateScreen();\n  }\n});\nonEvent(\"5_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  if (input.length < 4) {\n    input += \"5\";\n    updateScreen();\n  }\n});\nonEvent(\"6_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  if (input.length < 4) {\n    input += \"6\";\n    updateScreen();\n  }\n});\nonEvent(\"7_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  if (input.length < 4) {\n    input += \"7\";\n    updateScreen();\n  }\n});\nonEvent(\"8_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  if (input.length < 4) {\n    input += \"8\";\n    updateScreen();\n  }\n});\nonEvent(\"9_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  if (input.length < 4) {\n    input += \"9\";\n    updateScreen();\n  }\n});\nonEvent(\"0_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  if (input.length < 4) {\n    input += \"0\";\n    updateScreen();\n  }\n});\n\n// --- ENTER button ---\nonEvent(\"enter_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  var responseTime = simulateResponseTime(input, correctPIN);\n  var resultText = \"\";\n\n  if (input === correctPIN) {\n    resultText = \"✅ Correct\";\n  } else {\n    resultText = \"❌ Incorrect\";\n  }\n\n  setText(\"screen\", resultText);\n\n  // Log to separate areas\n  setText(\"attempt_area\", getText(\"attempt_area\") + input + \"\\n\");\n  setText(\"response_time_area\", getText(\"response_time_area\") + responseTime + \"s\\n\");\n\n  input = \"\";\n});\n\n// --- CLEAR button ---\nonEvent(\"clear_button\", \"click\", function() {\n  input = \"\";\n  updateScreen();\n});\n\n// --- Screen update function ---\nfunction updateScreen() {\n  setText(\"screen\", input);\n}\n\n\n",
    "start_html": "<div id=\"designModeViz\" class=\"appModern clip-content\" data-radium=\"true\" style=\"width: 600px; height: 450px; display: block;\"><div class=\"screen\" tabindex=\"1\" data-theme=\"default\" id=\"screen1\" style=\"display: block; height: 450px; width: 600px; left: 0px; top: 0px; position: absolute; z-index: 0; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img src=\"/level_starter_assets/ai-powered-threats-defenses-lesson10-side-channel-attack/vecteezy_realistic-keypad-of-an-automated-teller-machine-vector_35631481.jpg\" data-canonical-image-url=\"image://vecteezy_realistic-keypad-of-an-automated-teller-machine-vector_35631481.jpg\" data-image-type=\"file\" data-object-fit=\"contain\" id=\"pin_pad\" style=\"height: 265px; width: 335px; border-style: solid; border-width: 0px; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-radius: 0px; position: absolute; left: 5px; top: 130px; margin: 0px;\"><div contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"textArea\" id=\"screen\" style=\"width: 300px; height: 80px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgb(225, 241, 251); color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-color: rgb(28, 0, 0); border-radius: 2px; border-width: 4px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 22px; top: 60px; margin: 0px; font-size: 50px; text-align: right;\"></div><button id=\"1_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 41px; width: 55px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 47px; top: 171px;\">1</button><button id=\"2_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 41px; width: 55px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 105px; top: 171px;\">2</button><button id=\"3_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 41px; width: 55px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 165px; top: 171px;\">3</button><button id=\"4_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 41px; width: 55px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 47px; top: 220px;\">4</button><button id=\"7_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 41px; width: 55px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 47px; top: 265px;\">7</button><button id=\"5_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 41px; width: 55px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 105px; top: 220px;\">5</button><button id=\"8_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 41px; width: 55px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 105px; top: 265px;\">8</button><button id=\"9_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 41px; width: 55px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 165px; top: 265px;\">9</button><button id=\"6_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 41px; width: 55px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 165px; top: 220px;\">6</button><button id=\"0_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 41px; width: 55px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 105px; top: 310px;\">0</button><button id=\"enter_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 40px; width: 70px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 230px; top: 170px;\"></button><button id=\"clear_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 40px; width: 70px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 230px; top: 220px;\"></button><button id=\"cancel_button\" style=\"padding: 0px; margin: 0px; border-style: solid; height: 40px; width: 70px; background-color: rgba(255, 164, 0, 0); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-color: rgba(77, 87, 95, 0); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 1px; font-family: &quot;Arial Black&quot;, Gadget, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; position: absolute; left: 230px; top: 265px;\"></button><div contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"textArea\" id=\"attempt_area\" style=\"width: 120px; height: 325px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 2px; border-width: 1px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 335px; top: 60px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\"></div><label style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 320px; border-style: solid; text-rendering: optimizespeed; color: rgb(77, 87, 95); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding: 2px 15px; width: 120px; height: 20px; position: absolute; left: 335px; top: 30px; text-align: center;\" id=\"label2\">Attempt</label><div contenteditable=\"true\" class=\"textArea\" id=\"response_time_area\" style=\"width: 120px; height: 325px; border-style: solid; background-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border-radius: 2px; border-width: 1px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding: 5px 15px; position: absolute; left: 465px; top: 60px; margin: 0px; text-align: center;\"></div><label style=\"margin: 0px; line-height: 1; overflow: hidden; overflow-wrap: break-word; max-width: 320px; border-style: solid; text-rendering: optimizespeed; color: rgb(77, 87, 95); background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); border-color: rgb(77, 87, 95); border-radius: 0px; border-width: 0px; font-family: &quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; padding: 2px 15px; width: 129px; height: 20px; position: absolute; left: 460px; top: 30px; text-align: center;\" id=\"label3\">Response Time</label></div></div>",
    "long_instructions": "\r\n## **What Is a Side-Channel Attack?**\r\n\r\nA **side-channel attack** doesn't break encryption directly. Instead, it listens for *clues* from a system's behavior. These clues could include:\r\n\r\n* How long something takes to respond (timing)\r\n* How much power a device uses\r\n* Sounds, electromagnetic leaks, etc.\r\n\r\nEven if a password or PIN is encrypted, attackers can use **response timing** to figure out how close they are to the real one — character by character.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n### **Scenario: You're the Attacker**\r\n\r\nImagine you're trying to guess someone's 4-digit PIN. Each time you make a guess, the system responds **slightly faster** when early digits are correct. You're trying to learn the PIN by watching **response times** and making smart next guesses.\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Use the number pad to enter a 4-digit guess.\r\n\r\n2. Press **ENTER** to submit it.\r\n\r\n3. Your guess and the system's response time (in seconds) will appear on the right.\r\n\r\n4. Repeat with new guesses and look for small changes in response time.\r\n\r\n     * Longer times often mean you're getting more digits correct (especially early ones).\r\n\t* Don’t guess randomly. Use the response times to plan your next move.\r\n\t* What happens if you guess `1999`, then `2999`, then `3999`? Do you notice a difference in timing?\r\n    \r\n5. Keep going until you unlock the correct PIN!\r\n",
    "preload_asset_list": null
  },
